---
import { pageTitle } from '../../config/site';
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
	title={pageTitle('Booking details')}
	description="What we collect for a unified booking: party size, date, contact details, and pricing notes — aligned with the board’s BOOKING DETAILS (unified) block."
>
	<main id="main" class="main">
		<h1 class="title">Booking details (unified)</h1>
		<p class="lead">
			This page lists the fields the FigJam board called out for a single booking flow — implementation can connect to your
			PMS, Stripe metadata, or CRM later.
		</p>

		<section class="block" aria-labelledby="f-heading">
			<h2 id="f-heading" class="h2">Guest &amp; party</h2>
			<ul class="list">
				<li>Number of guests (adults, children, infants) — board note: headcount drives pricing tiers.</li>
				<li>Preferred date(s) and flexibility — calendar selection in the design notes.</li>
				<li>Contact: name, email, phone, language preference.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="block" aria-labelledby="p-heading">
			<h2 id="p-heading" class="h2">Price &amp; discounts</h2>
			<ul class="list">
				<li>Price calculator: adults / children / infants (e.g. infant 0–3 €0, children 4–10, adults — from board).</li>
				<li>Discount logic: board mentions including discounts in calculation — also note “nema popusta” for certain cases; clarify business rules before automating.</li>
				<li>Cave / park tickets: often <strong>not</strong> in base price — separate line on-site.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="block" aria-labelledby="o-heading">
			<h2 id="o-heading" class="h2">Offer delivery</h2>
			<ul class="list">
				<li>PDF offers, payment link, or QR code — for private quotes (per ops sticky notes).</li>
				<li>Stripe Checkout for online card payment when <code>CHECKOUT_MODE=stripe</code> and Price IDs exist.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="block" aria-labelledby="m-heading">
			<h2 id="m-heading" class="h2">After booking</h2>
			<ul class="list">
				<li>Meeting point details and “what to bring” confirmation email.</li>
				<li>Predefined messages for private tours — template library TBD.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<p>
			<a class="cta" href="/contact">Contact us</a> · <a href="/tours">Browse tours</a>
		</p>
	</main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
	.main {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 4rem;
	}

	.title {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
		color: var(--color-nav);
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.lead {
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}

	.block {
		margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
	}

	.h2 {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
		color: var(--color-nav);
	}

	.list {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	code {
		font-size: 0.9em;
		background: #f1f5f9;
		padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
		border-radius: 4px;
	}

	.cta {
		font-weight: 700;
	}
</style>
